title: Use burning wallet tokens to promote DAO
body:
Hello everyone, this proposal is to use 500 SPORE from the burner wallet to improve the new release of our Chieftains DAO module with an airdrop campaign on Twitter to giveaway those tokens in order to interact with the publication.

Rules and further details can be discussed on Discord.

- Burner Wallet: https://safe.spore.engineering/#/safes/0x79207f009733a9770edE24f7Fd7b8e02b2A25222

- Chieftain Medium Announcement: https://spore-eng.medium.com/introducing-the-chieftains-create-voting-proposals-approve-dao-expenses-automatically-9537c8cfada5
